<P>
NO PREVIEW FAN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Concerning Dirk and Erik Sanders' May 6 letter on movie previews: They are not 
alone. 
</P>
<P>
While viewing "Crocodile Dundee II" a couple of years ago, I realized I was 
totally bored. Why? All the best scenes and lines had already been shown in 
previews I had seen before the movie's opening. 
</P>
<P>
