TECHNOLOGY; INFORMATION STORAGE AND RETRIEVAL; EXPERTS; RESEARCH CENTERS; 
PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT; LAFALCE, JOHN J; INDUSTRIAL POLICY; LEGISLATION -- UNITED 
