right, "Robocop 2" and at the left, a logo from "Dick Tracy," ; Photo, Total 
Recall ; Photo, Flight of the Intruder ; Photo, Back to the Future III ; Photo, 
The Two Jakes ; Photo, Dick Tracy ; Photo, Gremlins II ; Photo, Days of Thunder 
; Photo, Presumed Innocent ; Photo, Ducktales The Movie: Treasure of the Lost 
