<TEXT>
<P>
My cable company has been collecting what they call an "Orange County Property 
Tax" from me for several months now. 
</P>
<P>
Would someone care to tell me what they're doing with the interest on my money? 
</P>
<P>
Cable companies have bad service, and we, the people, have no choice because 
they have a monopoly! 
</P>
<P>
EILEEN E. PADBERG 
</P>
<P>
