<HEADLINE>
<P>
GET TIPS ON SELLING HOME AT BUYERS FAIR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
One of the biggest obstacles to buying a new home can be selling your present 
house in today's soft real estate market. But don't despair, expert help is on 
the way. 
</P>
<P>
Fair-goers at this Saturday's Los Angeles Times Home Buyers Fair can 
participate in special two-hour round-table discussions with leading Orange 
County real estate experts and profit from their advice -- and tips from other 
home sellers. 
</P>
<P>
Realtors and other experts will talk with you and other frustrated sellers in 
small informal groups from 11 a.m. to 1 p.m. and discuss better ways to market 
your home, how to price it right, how to prepare it for sale and how to select 
and work with a real estate agent. 
</P>
<P>
For a guide to the fair, please see the second section of Real Estate. 
</P>
</TEXT>
