Maggio, were in court in Pasadena for his sentencing May 3. ; Photo, Crespin 
and Wheeler met via a pen-pal ad when he was in prison. ; Photo, Crespin in 
court, just four days before he committed suicide. LOU MACK / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
