<P>
EL TORO (CA) -- INCORPORATION; PORTOLA HILLS (CA) -- INCORPORATION; 
NEIGHBORHOODS; ORANGE COUNTY -- DEVELOPMENT AND REDEVELOPMENT 
</P>
