<HEADLINE>
<P>
FOR THE RECORD 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In a recent Mature Traveler column on San Francisco bargains for senior 
citizens, the minimum age to receive discount fares on the city's cable cars 
was incorrectly given as 62. the correct minimum age is 65. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
Correction 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
